1. Hover Effect:
Each .experience-item has a hover effect that shifts it slightly to the right (transform: translateX(10px)).

2. Details Visibility:
The details are initially hidden (display: none).
On hover, the .details div becomes visible (display: block) with a sliding animation.

3. Keyframe Animation:
The slideIn animation makes the text appear smoothly when the .details div is revealed.

3. General Styling:
Styling for headers, paragraphs, and containers to ensure readability and visual appeal.